### AUTHENTICATION EXAMPLES

### 1. CLIENT LOGIN (Public - No Auth Required)
POST http://app.xycargo.com/v1/auth/client/login HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### RESPONSE
{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "client_id": 1,
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "phone": "+233501234567",
    "address": "Accra, Ghana",
    "company": "ABC Corp"
  },
  "token": "eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..."
}

### 2. ACCESS PROTECTED ROUTE (With Bearer Token)
GET http://app.xycargo.com/v1/protected/profile HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...

### RESPONSE
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "This is a protected route",
  "user": {
    "data": {
      "client_id": 1,
      "firstName": "John",
      "lastName": "Doe",
      "email": "john.doe@example.com",
      "phone": "+233501234567",
      "address": "Accra, Ghana",
      "company": "ABC Corp"
    },
    "iat": 1697880000,
    "exp": 1697883600
  }
}

### 3. ACCESS WITHOUT TOKEN (Should Fail)
GET http://app.xycargo.com/v1/protected/profile HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive

### RESPONSE
{
  "status": "error",
  "code": 401,
  "message": "Authorization header is required"
}

### 4. ACCESS WITH INVALID TOKEN (Should Fail)
GET http://app.xycargo.com/v1/protected/profile HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive
Authorization: Bearer invalid.jwt.token

### RESPONSE
{
  "status": "error",
  "code": 401,
  "message": "Invalid or expired token"
}

### 5. ACCESS WITH MALFORMED AUTH HEADER (Should Fail)
GET http://app.xycargo.com/v1/protected/profile HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive
Authorization: NotBearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...

### RESPONSE
{
  "status": "error",
  "code": 401,
  "message": "Invalid authorization header format. Expected: Bearer <token>"
}

### 6. PUBLIC ROUTE (No Auth Required)
GET http://app.xycargo.com/v1/public/status HTTP/1.1
Host: app.xycargo.com
Connection: keep-alive

### RESPONSE
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "This is a public route - no authentication required"
}

